00:01:39,581 --> 00:01:40,974
Just work here.

16
00:01:40,975 --> 00:01:41,851
Hey!

17
00:01:41,852 --> 00:01:44,228
I sent you up there to save people, and you come back hurt?

18
00:01:44,229 --> 00:01:46,981
She was all I had...

19
00:01:48,066 --> 00:01:49,341
Because of me...

20
00:01:49,341 --> 00:01:51,170
They died because of me.

21
00:01:51,170 --> 00:01:53,730
[No Entrance, Danger of Collapse]

