23
00:01:55,681 --> 00:01:57,157
That man...

24
00:01:57,158 --> 00:01:58,960
He killed them.

25
00:01:58,960 --> 00:02:00,144
Black Bridge Valley Village...

26
00:02:00,144 --> 00:02:01,478
That was the name.

27
00:02:01,478 --> 00:02:03,105
Black Bridge Valley Village...

28
00:02:03,105 --> 00:02:04,565
Why do you ask out of the blue?

29
00:02:04,565 --> 00:02:06,692
What on earth was going on in that village?

30
00:02:06,692 --> 00:02:09,461
Some residents lost their lives,

31
