All those who died till now had lived in this village.

35
00:02:18,454 --> 00:02:20,598
What really happened back then?

36
00:02:20,598 --> 00:02:22,650
[3:00 p.m. at the Black Bridge Valley]

37
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:24,543
Black Bridge Valley

38
00:02:24,543 --> 00:02:27,354
Hyun Jo went there just before the accident.

39
00:02:27,355 --> 00:02:28,856
Please take me there.

40
00:02:28,857 --> 00:02:30,649
Will Yi Kang be all right by herself?

41
00:02:30,650 --> 00:02:31,617
Senior Yi Kang...

42
00:02:31,617 --> 00:02:33,811
Senior Yi Kang is on the mountain.

43
00:02:59,762 --> 00:03:02,247
- Hurry up!
- Will Yi Kang be all right by herself?

44
00:03:02,247 --> 00:03:04,850
Let's rescue the lost first and quickly head back.

45
00:03:16,554 --> 00:03:19,223
Huh? Wasn't it here?

46
00:03:19,223 --> 00:03:20,557
Why is no one here?

47
00:03:20,557 --> 00:03:24,228
Haedong One. We're at Magpie Hill, but there's no one here.

48
00:03:24,228 --> 00:03:27,089
Look carefully. You're at the right place.

49
00:03:28,691 --> 00:03:31,177
There's not a single soul here.

50
00:03:34,422 --> 00:03:36,965
Someone made a false report.

51
00:03:36,966 --> 00:03:38,534
What?

52
00:03:40,161 --> 00:03:43,306
Someone made a false report, so that Yi Kang was left alone.

53
00:04:22,900 --> 00:04:26,440
[Caution]
[Asian black bear protection area]

54
00:04:40,947 --> 00:04:42,698
You finally came...

55
00:04:49,247 --> 00:04:52,074
Can you see me?

56
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:58,990
♫ A deeper day ♫

57
00:04:58,990 --> 00:05:02,817
What happened to you?

58
00:05:02,817 --> 00:05:05,345
Were you badly hurt?

59
00:05:05,346 --> 00:05:07,048
Does it...

60
00:05:08,099 --> 00:05:10,109
still hurt?

61
00:05:11,769 --> 00:05:14,479
I saw a guy with a ranger's uniform.

62
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:17,232
It was definitely a winter suit.

63
00:05:17,233 --> 00:05:20,286
His hands and clothes were covered in blood.

64
00:05:25,260 --> 00:05:31,010
♫ The place that is still breathing ♫

65
00:05:31,010 --> 00:05:34,810
♫ I have to get closer to that place ♫

66
00:05:34,810 --> 00:05:37,353
He looked very lonely.

67
00:05:39,005 --> 00:05:41,406
He heard your voice on the radio...

68
00:05:41,406 --> 00:05:42,841
Da Won!

69
00:05:42,842 --> 00:05:46,695
And I think he desperately wanted to talk to you.

70
00:05:49,515 --> 00:05:52,309
It felt like...

71
00:05:52,309 --> 00:05:54,937
he had waited a long time for you.

72
00:05:56,781 --> 00:05:58,682
Senior Yi Kang...

73
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:03,904
Why have you been like this?

74
00:06:03,905 --> 00:06:07,933
Left alone like a fool, unable to leave...

75
00:06:07,933 --> 00:06:10,536
What have you been doing?

76
00:06:14,207 --> 00:06:16,500
Last summer...

77
00:06:16,501 --> 00:06:20,270
What happened to you since then?

78
00:06:27,020 --> 00:06:32,030
[2019]

79
00:07:05,508 --> 00:07:07,342
It was you?

80
00:07:07,343 --> 00:07:09,202
Have you been killing people all this time?

81
00:07:09,202 --> 00:07:11,355
What do you mean, killing people?

82
00:07:11,355 --> 00:07:12,739
- Why are you here?
- What do you—?

83
00:07:12,739 --> 00:07:14,875
Why did you come here?

84
00:07:16,936 --> 00:07:18,728
To meet someone.

85
00:07:18,729 --> 00:07:21,523
Who? Were you also going to kill that person, too?

86
00:07:21,524 --> 00:07:23,692
What on earth are you saying?

87
00:07:23,693 --> 00:07:27,521
I already know everything, so answer me.

88
00:07:34,996 --> 00:07:37,497
I don't know why you're doing this,

89
00:07:37,498 --> 00:07:40,251
but I didn't come to kill anyone.

90
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:43,646
I came because someone called me here.

91
00:07:44,297 --> 00:07:49,006
Someone called you here?

92
00:07:54,432 --> 00:07:56,500
See for yourself.

93
00:08:05,300 --> 00:08:09,690
[3:00 p.m. at the Black Bridge Valley]

94
00:08:11,057 --> 00:08:13,183
Kim Eung Soon.

95
00:08:13,183 --> 00:08:15,202
This...

96
00:08:15,203 --> 00:08:17,746
was your phone?

97
00:08:17,746 --> 00:08:19,265
Yes.

98
00:08:20,124 --> 00:08:22,018
It's mine.

99
00:08:26,072 --> 00:08:28,249
What's going on?

100
00:08:33,329 --> 00:08:35,220
So, Sergeant Kim...

101
00:08:35,890 --> 00:08:38,526
called you here?

102
00:08:41,395 --> 00:08:43,021
Yes.

103
00:08:43,022 --> 00:08:44,940
Why did he want to see you here?

104
00:08:44,941 --> 00:08:48,777
I don't know. He's the one who called me here.

105
00:08:48,778 --> 00:08:52,155
I've waited for nearly an hour, but he's neither here, nor answering my call.

106
00:08:52,156 --> 00:08:54,491
So I decided to look around.

107
00:08:54,492 --> 00:08:56,652
The fact that he's still not here...

108
00:08:57,787 --> 00:09:00,247
Maybe he forgot,

109
00:09:00,248 --> 00:09:02,767
or something else came up.

110
00:09:12,830 --> 00:09:17,550
[Geriatric Hospital]

111
00:09:25,381 --> 00:09:28,667
It was probably about Black Bridge Valley,

112
00:09:28,667 --> 00:09:30,961
if he wanted to meet here.

113
00:09:33,197 --> 00:09:36,383
We often ran into each other here.

114
00:09:36,383 --> 00:09:38,911
I think he misses this place very much, too.

115
00:09:39,578 --> 00:09:41,897
Is Sergeant Kim...

116
00:09:41,897 --> 00:09:44,650
also from here?

117
00:09:46,319 --> 00:09:48,445
That's right.

118
00:09:48,445 --> 00:09:50,822
Black Bridge Valley Village...

119
00:09:50,822 --> 00:09:53,250
is his hometown, too.

120
00:10:09,567 --> 00:10:12,494
- Get out of here!
- Please stop!

121
00:10:12,494 --> 00:10:16,123
We have no intention of moving out. Leave.

122
00:10:16,699 --> 00:10:18,308
I told you we'll give you

123
00:10:18,308 --> 00:10:21,661
as much relocation compensation as possible.

124
00:10:21,662 --> 00:10:24,348
We have no further business. Please leave.

125
00:10:24,348 --> 00:10:25,774
Let's go.

126
00:10:26,292 --> 00:10:28,169
You'll...

127
00:10:29,570 --> 00:10:32,039
absolutely regret this.

128
00:10:33,491 --> 00:10:34,841
As the mayor of this village,

129
00:10:34,842 --> 00:10:37,244
I'm strongly against the cable car business.

130
00:10:37,244 --> 00:10:39,355
What does everyone think?

131
00:10:45,002 --> 00:10:47,170
What's your opinion, Hyeon Su's father?

132
00:10:47,170 --> 00:10:50,090
If that's what you think,

133
00:10:50,090 --> 00:10:52,234
I'm sure it's right.

134
00:10:52,234 --> 00:10:54,094
What about you, Se Wook's father?

135
00:10:54,094 --> 00:10:57,173
I'll do as you say.

136
00:10:58,558 --> 00:10:59,975
But...

137
00:10:59,975 --> 00:11:03,019
How much is the compensation?

138
00:11:03,019 --> 00:11:07,399
Who cares? We must protect our hometown, our mountain.

139
00:11:12,004 --> 00:11:13,655
And you, Eung Soon's father?

140
00:11:13,655 --> 00:11:16,876
I'll follow Sol's father lead, too.

141
00:11:17,593 --> 00:11:19,394
Everyone else?

142
00:11:25,351 --> 00:11:27,044
Me, too.

143
00:11:36,570 --> 00:11:40,174
- We're back!
- We're here.

144
00:11:41,534 --> 00:11:43,544
How was school, guys?

145
00:11:51,979 --> 00:11:56,390
Seems like the oldest, Eung Soon, is the captain there.

146
00:12:04,930 --> 00:12:09,190
[Gaeam site]

147
00:12:09,190 --> 00:12:11,140
[Daesung site]

148
