00:20:00,949 --> 00:20:05,202
She left after she filed a theft report?

250
00:20:05,203 --> 00:20:06,688
Yeah.

251
00:20:06,688 --> 00:20:09,166
She said to call her if we need anything.

252
00:20:10,400 --> 00:20:12,603
Okay. Let's go.

253
00:20:12,603 --> 00:20:16,005
Can we take a break for a minute?

254
00:20:16,006 --> 00:20:20,202
You're not even a ranger. Why are you so good at mountain climbing?

255
00:20:20,202 --> 00:20:23,597
He's way better than us.

256
00:20:23,597 --> 00:20:26,808
Did something happen? You don't look good.

257
00:20:28,669 --> 00:20:32,172
No, it's nothing. We're leaving.

258
00:20:32,172 --> 00:20:33,673
Okay.

259
00:20:37,361 --> 00:20:42,007
Someone who's close to the rangers and knows the mountain well.

260
00:20:53,543 --> 00:20:56,163
- Illegal herb collecting?
- Yes.

261
00:21:02,094 --> 00:21:04,371
Where's Sergeant Kim?

262
00:21:04,371 --> 00:21:06,306
He's on patrol.

263
00:21:07,624 --> 00:21:10,127
That's a lot of herbs.

264
00:21:10,127 --> 00:21:13,882
Where do you find so much of them?

265
00:21:13,882 --> 00:21:18,343
I was just wondering. How's the investigation going

266
00:21:18,343 --> 00:21:21,113
on the bus accident during last summer's flood?

267
00:21:22,197 --> 00:21:24,433
The bus accident?

268
00:21:24,433 --> 00:21:27,786
I heard you were investigating it.

269
00:21:28,887 --> 00:21:33,616
It was concluded as a simple accident.

270
00:21:33,616 --> 00:21:37,045
Sergeant Kim sent in the report himself.

271
00:21:39,698 --> 00:21:43,827
Can I see the daily log during the recent flood?

272
00:21:43,827 --> 00:21:46,512
I thought maybe we can find witnesses

273
