00:28:49,820 --> 00:28:57,690
♫ Through the gaps in time, I hear you. ♫

346
00:28:59,446 --> 00:29:02,239
Hey, Kang Hyun Jo!

347
00:29:02,239 --> 00:29:05,974
Great work! How are you doing?

348
00:29:05,974 --> 00:29:09,562
Is he treating you well?

349
00:29:14,069 --> 00:29:15,335
Ah, that's better.

350
00:29:15,336 --> 00:29:18,964
I heard kids at Cheongsan Retreat were training near Cheonwang Peak.

351
00:29:18,965 --> 00:29:20,466
I wonder if they went down okay.

352
00:29:20,467 --> 00:29:24,387
Some went down, and some are still near Cheongwang Peak.

