00:29:40,945 --> 00:29:43,739
You seem to be searching for something.

354
00:29:43,740 --> 00:29:46,008
Did you lose something?

355
00:29:47,620 --> 00:29:50,730
Well... A military dog tag.

356
00:29:50,730 --> 00:29:53,040
Why are you looking for that on the mountain?

