367
00:30:25,323 --> 00:30:29,493
A snake trap, hiking pole, ropes, crampons...

368
00:30:29,494 --> 00:30:31,662
I thought nobody went up there.

369
00:30:31,663 --> 00:30:33,413
Who threw all that?

370
00:30:33,414 --> 00:30:37,610
Maybe... Could it be?

371
00:30:37,610 --> 00:30:39,211
There's a pole.

372
00:30:39,212 --> 00:30:41,672
It must've belonged to one of the illegal hikers.

373
00:30:41,673 --> 00:30:44,425
There are more, like crampons.

374
00:30:46,761 --> 00:30:49,429
A military dog tag, ropes.

375
00:30:49,430 --> 00:30:51,932
Crampons, hiking poles.

376
00:30:51,933 --> 00:30:55,236
Hiking shoes, snake trap.

377
00:30:55,728 --> 00:30:58,605
Hyun Jo! Kang Hyun Jo!

378
00:30:58,606 --> 00:31:00,049
Are you okay?

379
00:31:01,401 --> 00:31:04,345
Who cleaned out the things in the shelter?

380
00:31:04,345 --> 00:31:05,946
Who was it?

381
00:31:05,947 --> 00:31:09,850
It was probably the Moojin Station rangers.

382
00:31:14,873 --> 00:31:18,026
- Black Bridge Valley Shelter?
- Yes.

383
00:31:18,026 --> 00:31:21,253
I heard you cleaned out the lost articles in there.

384
00:31:21,254 --> 00:31:23,672
Us? No, we didn't.

385
00:31:23,673 --> 00:31:26,717
We went in to clean but it was already done.

386
00:31:26,718 --> 00:31:30,304
Maybe it was the team from the Main Station.

387
00:31:30,305 --> 00:31:33,473
They'd come, too? Who else was there?

388
00:31:33,474 --> 00:31:37,519
Us and Bidam Shelter, Main Station, Seseok Station.

389
00:31:37,520 --> 00:31:40,489
The Ecology Evaluation Center? They also came.

390
00:31:42,525 --> 00:31:43,927
Yes.

391
00:31:43,927 --> 00:31:47,071
The lost articles from the Black Bridge Valley Shelter.

392
00:31:50,950 --> 00:31:53,653
Yes. I understand.

393
00:32:03,500 --> 00:32:06,540
[List of Rangers on the Asian black bear caution notice installation team]

394
00:32:13,056 --> 00:32:16,692
No one seems to have touched the lost articles there.

