00:32:34,460 --> 00:32:38,389
The rangers already took all the lost articles near here.

397
00:32:39,374 --> 00:32:43,611
Why did they throw all these away in this deep forest?

398
00:32:43,611 --> 00:32:45,796
Get some help and take care of these.

399
00:32:45,797 --> 00:32:47,548
Yes, Sir.

400
00:33:20,373 --> 00:33:23,984
It was the criminal. He took them.

