00:38:51,479 --> 00:38:56,041
I can't tell you because this is hard to believe for anyone.

450
00:38:56,042 --> 00:39:00,295
Thank you for trusting me and doing as I've asked you to.

451
00:39:00,296 --> 00:39:03,174
But can you please trust me?

452
00:39:06,385 --> 00:39:10,113
Just once more?

453
00:39:15,186 --> 00:39:17,004
All right.

454
00:39:17,004 --> 00:39:19,189
Do we just need to install a video camera?

455
00:39:19,190 --> 00:39:20,357
Yes.

456
00:39:20,358 --> 00:39:23,610
And stay there.

457
00:39:23,611 --> 00:39:27,456
You must stop him before he kills another person.

458
00:39:28,074 --> 00:39:31,735
Anything else?

