485
00:42:00,960 --> 00:42:03,586
Okay. But...

486
00:42:03,586 --> 00:42:07,590
Please keep this a secret from the others.

487
00:42:07,590 --> 00:42:09,351
Of course.

488
00:44:24,995 --> 00:44:28,281
Today, I must...

489
00:44:29,124 --> 00:44:31,670
...Catch the criminal.

490
00:44:46,200 --> 00:44:47,433
Go inside.

491
00:44:47,434 --> 00:44:50,286
Call me immediately, if anything happens.

492
00:44:53,299 --> 00:44:55,192
We'll be right back.

